          "id": "project-solace",
          "title": "Solace Wellness - Brand Identity",
          "path": "/work/solace-wellness-rebrand",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>Solace Wellness approached us to create a brand identity that would convey calm, trust, and modern sophistication for their chain of premium wellness centers.</p><h2>The Brief</h2><p>Solace needed a complete visual identity system that would work across physical signage, digital platforms, and print collateral. The brand had to feel elevated yet approachable, reflecting their philosophy that wellness is for everyone.</p><h2>Our Approach</h2><p>We developed a warm, earthy color palette paired with clean typography and organic geometric forms. The logomark -- an abstracted lotus rendered in continuous line -- symbolizes growth, balance, and interconnection.</p><h2>Deliverables</h2><ul><li>Primary and secondary logo systems</li><li>Color palette and typography guidelines</li><li>Stationery suite and print collateral</li><li>Environmental graphics for 8 locations</li><li>Digital brand guidelines document</li></ul>",
