        {
          "__typename": "NodeProject",
          "id": "project-atlas",
          "title": "Atlas Fintech - Digital Platform",
          "path": "/work/atlas-fintech-platform",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>Atlas Fintech needed a complete redesign of their investment platform to improve user engagement, simplify complex financial data, and increase conversion from free to premium tiers.</p><h2>The Challenge</h2><p>The existing platform suffered from information overload, inconsistent UI patterns, and a confusing onboarding flow. User research revealed that 60% of new signups abandoned the platform within the first week.</p><h2>Our Solution</h2><p>We redesigned the entire experience using a progressive disclosure model. New users see a simplified dashboard that gradually introduces advanced features as they become more comfortable. Data visualizations were rebuilt with clarity as the primary goal.</p><h2>Results</h2><ul><li>First-week retention improved from 40% to 72%</li><li>Free-to-premium conversion increased by 85%</li><li>Average session time grew from 4 to 11 minutes</li><li>NPS score rose from 32 to 67</li></ul>",
            "summary": "Atlas Fintech needed a complete redesign of their investment platform to improve user engagement, simplify complex financial data, and increase conversion from free to premium tiers.The ChallengeThe e"
