        {
          "__typename": "NodeProject",
          "id": "project-terraverde",
          "title": "TerraVerde - Packaging Design",
          "path": "/work/terraverde-packaging",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>TerraVerde, an organic skincare brand, commissioned us to design packaging for their new product line that would stand out on shelves while communicating their commitment to sustainability.</p><h2>Design Philosophy</h2><p>We drew inspiration from botanical illustration traditions, creating detailed line drawings of the key ingredients in each product. The illustrations are printed with vegetable-based inks on recycled paperboard, reinforcing the brand's environmental values through every material choice.</p><h2>Sustainability</h2><ul><li>100% recycled and recyclable packaging materials</li><li>Vegetable-based inks throughout</li><li>Minimalist design to reduce material waste</li><li>Refill program branding and in-store display system</li></ul>",
            "summary": "TerraVerde, an organic skincare brand, commissioned us to design packaging for their new product line that would stand out on shelves while communicating their commitment to sustainability.Design Phil"
